In re Resignation of App.

[Cite as In re Resignation of App (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1215.]

(No. 92-880 Submitted May 12, 1992 Decided May 13, 1992.)

The resignation of Robert Philip App as an attorney, Registration No. 0027874, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
